  "detailed_description": "Moe is a 3D story-driven adventure-platformer with unique wonderful world, breathtaking atmosphere and fun fast-paced action.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>MAIN FEATURES</i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fun movement</strong> mechanics, that you can use in unique environments and engaging platformer-like puzzles.<br></li><li><strong>Exciting combat</strong>, where you can use a variety of abilities, weapons and meet extraordinary opponents.<br></li><li><strong>\"Reality Break\"</strong>, use the powers to manipulate the existence of this world - create temporary objects to use in puzzles and combat.<br></li><li><strong>Progress</strong>, your abilities and skills in simple but emergent parts of gameplay.</li></ul>",
